{"tid":858540,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"終於撐不住了！黑龍江最大鋼企破產、副市長接管","createTime":"2018-10-12T01:18:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T06:19:33.000Z","uid":32511,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"96e52684c37bc0f9caec314dae093ab401570a32","tid":858540,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T01:18:19.000Z","msg":"中國黑龍江省最大鋼企「西林鋼鐵」曾負債近240億元人民幣（約1091億元新台幣），雖然近年虧損減少，但仍撐不下去，根據中媒報導，西林鋼鐵已向法院申請破產重整，伊春市中級法院11日已裁定受理此案，按照規定，指定西林鋼鐵清算組擔任西林鋼鐵管理人，負責人則由伊春市副市長張國軍來擔任。<br />\n <br />\n中國媒體《新京報》報導，上述清算組或管理人具有一定的權限，像管理人的職務為接管債務人財產、印章和帳簿等文書資料，也決定債務人的內部管理事務，管理和處分債務人的財產等。<br />\n <br />\n西林鋼鐵創建於1966年，2005年改至為民營企業，旗下有多間子公司，2012年時具有年產700萬噸粗鋼的生產能力，在2012年名列中國企業500強的459位、中國民企500強的125位。<br />\n <br />\n不過西林鋼鐵早在2014年就被媒體披露過有破產危機，根據當年報導，西林鋼鐵截至2012年底負債總額接近240億元人民幣，資產負債率為99.78%，到2014年第1季負債雖有下降，但仍約有190億元人民幣（約864億元新台幣）。<br />\n <br />\n雖然西林鋼鐵近年虧損減少，但資金短缺問題仍未解決，負債、財務成本居高不下，總體形勢仍然嚴峻。"},{"pid":"e1771a201ca8754f8cfad3d56eefd0a19bd257a7","tid":858540,"uid":189093,"like":34,"dislike":2,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T01:37:31.000Z","msg":"名都衰過人<br />\n閪冧鋼材<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbe22c994280099437ab5fcb116ef027522877c7","tid":858540,"uid":96486,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T01:39:08.000Z","msg":"一層一層咁貪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2857ee47a8cbccb0823e892cc5b9ca7b4c02e4a3","tid":858540,"uid":39855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T01:46:47.000Z","msg":"騰龍換鳥，中国又贏！"},{"pid":"323f3a2f7a7840e73c71400e504d23e3ff3bdee3","tid":858540,"uid":26770,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T01:47:17.000Z","msg":"中國產能過盛&gt;香港起人工島"},{"pid":"1917a406d0880f3d3cefa526ba7099425a7bc3b4","tid":858540,"uid":10101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T01:53:44.000Z","msg":"點解次次都係鋼鐵廠出事"},{"pid":"b1615df5a57e1ca61ed285990e09a5f495164348","tid":858540,"uid":171866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1917a406d0880f3d3cefa526ba7099425a7bc3b4","tid":858540,"uid":10101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T01:53:44.000Z","msg":"點解次次都係鋼鐵廠出事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T04:52:02.000Z","msg":"本身係蝕住賣"},{"pid":"289978bfa3210e586a974bc4757161c3d3a3a118","tid":858540,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b1615df5a57e1ca61ed285990e09a5f495164348","tid":858540,"uid":171866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1917a406d0880f3d3cefa526ba7099425a7bc3b4","tid":858540,"uid":10101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T01:53:44.000Z","msg":"點解次次都係鋼鐵廠出事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T04:52:02.000Z","msg":"本身係蝕住賣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T06:39:53.000Z","msg":"接左間廠之後<br />\n伊春會<br />\n1：做番起，Fatfat<br />\n2 : 食200億債同一個無底洞，用五險一金去填"},{"pid":"5c5a306e753dfa13dba2d74166e8cdaa84aae1d8","tid":858540,"uid":195944,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T06:48:56.000Z","msg":"點解唔等多一陣<br />\n<br />\n香港同胞好快有一兆送俾大陸閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b4b697cbbe47b49eaa486483ead36215372918a","tid":858540,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T06:51:04.000Z","msg":"點先可以虧損240億。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6bd6a26c89f9bbcdf4412f9f85b8ef74094c667","tid":858540,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b4b697cbbe47b49eaa486483ead36215372918a","tid":858540,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T06:51:04.000Z","msg":"點先可以虧損240億。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T07:08:50.000Z","msg":"粗鋼冇價值<br />\n又要keep住營運<br />\n唯有不斷借錢"},{"pid":"fa12421c182d225a0a553075d22ad1f